 WebsiteDefender is now ready for the official release and available for purchase as of today!<span id=\"more-4419\"></span></p>\n<p>The Multi-Site Edition includes daily security checks for up to 50 websites per account with this number set to increase with future updates. Up next on our roadmap, WebsiteDefender will include more exciting features such as the ability to fully back-up and restore your WordPress blogs and websites. If you plan to monitor more than 50 websites, please contact <a title=\"The WebsiteDefender Sales Team\" href=\"mailto:sales@websitedefender.com\">The WebsiteDefender Team</a> .  The monthly fee for scanning multiple websites daily, using WebsiteDefender starts at just $5 per website.</p>\n<p>If you are scanning multiple websites, please <a title=\"WebsiteDefender Dashboard\" href=\"https://dashboard.websitedefender.com/\">login to your WebsiteDefender Dashboard</a> by the 29<sup>th</sup> February 2012 to renew your account and purchase a WebsiteDefender Subscription. Payment can be made by Credit Card or PayPal. Once you have completed the purchase, your account will instantly be updated to allow the multi-website feature.</p>\n<p>If you already have a multiple website account and would like to only scan a single website weekly, this is free of charge, however you will need to <a title=\"Sign up for a WebsiteDefender account\" href=\"https://dashboard.websitedefender.com/register-for-free-website-scan.php\">create a new WebsiteDefender account</a>. This step must be carried out in order for your service to continue without interruption. From  1<sup>st</sup> March 2012, beta users who are scanning multiple websites will no longer be able to secure them without a WebsiteDefender Subscription, as their accounts will be deactivated.</p>\n<p>For any questions regarding a WebsiteDefender Pricing Plan, please contact <a title=\"The WebsiteDefender Sales Team\" href=\"mailto:sales@websitedefender.com\">sales@websitedefender.com</a>.</p>\n<p>Stay 