\n<code>Choose a random color</code>\r\n\r\nAfter this, the software goes:\r\n\r\n<code>Move the rectangle</code>\r\n\r\n<code>Rotate the rectangle</code>\r\n\r\n<code>Increase the Hue of the rectangle by 1</code>\r\n\r\n<code>Place the text (this time, smaller)</code>\r\n\r\n<code>Repeat</code>\r\n\r\nThe idea is to create a system that is able to be used continually in many different settings. The poster is dynamic and can change at any moment. Also, each poster created is, in its own way, unique. This serves as a methodology in which digital design can achieve something that is basically impossible in its analog counterpart, yet retains some of that uniqueness that is so appealing about analog design.\r\n\r\nThis idea of creating systems of visual design that are dynamic is what I wish to explore in my thesis. More specifically, I wish to explore the relationship between content and form in these systems.\r\n\r\nThese were the final posters selected (in digital format):\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://thejsj.com/portfolio/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/SystemPoster.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-720\" title=\"SystemPoster\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://thejsj.com/portfolio/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/SystemPoster-221x300.png\" width=\"221\" height=\"300\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://thejsj.com/portfolio/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/SystemPoster2.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-721\" title=\"SystemPoster2\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://thejsj.com/portfolio/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/SystemPoster2-223x300.png\" width=\"223\" height=\"300\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://thejsj.com/portfolio/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/SystemPoster3.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-722\" title=\"SystemPoster3\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://thejsj.com/portfolio/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/SystemPoster3-221x300.png\" width=\"221\" height=\"300\" /></a>\r\n\r\nThis gallery shows the poster out there in the world, printed in some parts of VCU:\r\n\r\n[gallery id=\"719\" link=\"file\" exclude=\"720,721,722\"]','A Poster is a Sytem','','publish','closed','closed','','a-poster-is-a-sytem','','','2013-10-19 04:18:57','2013-10-19 04:18:57','',0,'http://thejsj.com/?post_type=piece&#038;p=719',14,'piece','',0),(720,1,'2012-04-02 18:44:47','2012-04-02 18:44:47','','SystemPoster','','inherit','open','open','','systemposter','','','2012-04-02 18:44:47','2012-04-02 18:44:47','',719,'http://thejsj.com/portfolio/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/SystemPoster.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(721,1,'2012-04-02 18:45:00','2012-04-02 18:45:00','','SystemPoster2','','inherit','open','open','','systemposter2','','','2012-04-02 18:45:00','2012-04-02 18:45:00','',719,'http://thejsj.com/portfolio/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/SystemPoster2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(722,1,'2012-04-02 18:48:56','2012-04-02 18:48:56','','SystemPoster3','','inherit','open','open','','systemposter3','','','2012-04-02 18:48:56','2012-04-02 18:48:56','',719,'http://thejsj.com/portfolio/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/SystemPoster3.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(723,1,'2012-04-02 19:00:36','2012-04-02 19:00:36','','DSC_0001','','inherit','open','open','','dsc_0001','','','2012-04-02 19:00:36','2012-04-02 19:00:36','',719,'http://thejsj.com/portfolio/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/DSC_0001.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(724,1,'2012-04-02 19:00:41','2012-04-02 19:00:41','','DSC_0004','','inherit','open','open','','dsc_0004-2','','','2012-04-02 19:00:41','2012-04-02 19:00:41','',719,'http://thejsj.com/portfolio/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/DSC_0004.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(725,1,'2012-04-02 19:00:46','2012-04-02 19:00:46','','DSC_0005','','inherit','open','open','','dsc_0005','','','2012-04-02 19:00:46','2012-04-02 19:00:46','',719,'http://thejsj.com/portfolio/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/DSC_0005.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(726,1,'2012-04-02 19:00:53','2012-04-02 19:00:53','','DSC_0006','','inherit','open','open','','dsc_0006','','','2012-04-02 19:00:53',