distance information for every single route.\r\n\r\nInstead of providing the user with the answer to this question, the project provides a way for the user to find out for himself. The question turns into a game of finding out the quickest route between several places.\r\n\r\nTaken from http://npossibleroutes.info/\r\n','N! Possible Routes','','publish','closed','closed','','n-possible-routes','','','2013-05-30 18:31:10','2013-05-30 18:31:10','',0,'http://thejsj.com/?post_type=piece&#038;p=1072',0,'piece','',0),(1073,1,'2013-01-10 20:33:26','2013-01-10 20:33:26','','naaa','','inherit','open','open','','naaa','','','2013-01-10 20:33:26','2013-01-10 20:33:26','',1072,'http://thejsj.com/portfolio/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/naaa.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(1074,1,'2013-01-10 20:33:32','2013-01-10 20:33:32','','step2','','inherit','open','open','','step2','','','2013-01-10 20:33:32','2013-01-10 20:33:32','',1072,'http://thejsj.com/portfolio/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/step2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(1075,1,'2013-01-10 20:33:50','2013-01-10 20:33:50','','n1','','inherit','open','open','','n1','','','2013-01-10 20:33:50','2013-01-10 20:33:50','',1072,'http://thejsj.com/portfolio/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/n1.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(1076,1,'2013-01-10 20:34:13','2013-01-10 20:34:13','','n2','','inherit','open','open','','n2','','','2013-01-10 20:34:13','2013-01-10 20:34:13','',1072,'http://thejsj.com/portfolio/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/n2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(1077,1,'2013-01-10 20:34:34','2013-01-10 20:34:34','','n3','','inherit','open','open','','n3','','','2013-01-10 20:34:34','2013-01-10 20:34:34','',1072,'http://thejsj.com/portfolio/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/n3.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(1078,1,'2013-01-10 20:34:49','2013-01-10 20:34:49','','n4','','inherit','open','open','','n4','','','2013-01-10 20:34:49','2013-01-10 20:34:49','',1072,'http://thejsj.com/portfolio/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/n4.png',0,'attachment','