ello-world/</a>\r\n<h4>Screenshots:</h4>\r\n<a href=\"http://thejsj.com/portfolio/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/screenshot1.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-1413\" alt=\"screenshot1\" src=\"http://thejsj.com/portfolio/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/screenshot1.png\" width=\"693\" height=\"639\" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://thejsj.com/portfolio/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/scr2.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-1414\" alt=\"scr2\" src=\"http://thejsj.com/portfolio/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/scr2.png\" width=\"581\" height=\"441\" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://thejsj.com/portfolio/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/sc3.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-1415\" alt=\"sc3\" src=\"http://thejsj.com/portfolio/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/sc3.png\" width=\"586\" height=\"382\" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nOptions Page:\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://thejsj.com/portfolio/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/JSJ-·-Gallery-Slideshow-Options-‹-N-Possible-Routes-—-WordPress1.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-1412\" alt=\"JSJ · Gallery &amp; Slideshow Options ‹ N! Possible Routes — WordPress(1)\" src=\"http://thejsj.com/portfolio/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/JSJ-·-Gallery-Slideshow-Options-‹-N-Possible-Routes-—-WordPress1-794x1024.png\" width=\"794\" height=\"1024\" /></a>\r\n<h3>Donate</h3>\r\nIf you find this plugin useful, don\'t hesitate to make a donation.\r\n<form action=\"https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr\" method=\"post\" target=\"_top\">\r\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"cmd\" value=\"_s-xclick\">\r\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"hosted_button_id\" value=\"3XAWNUDYDANUC\">\r\n<input type=\"image\" src=\"https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/btn/btn_donateCC_LG.gif\" border=\"0\" name=\"submit\" alt=\"PayPal - The safer, easier way to pay online!\">\r\n<img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/scr/pixel.gif\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\">\r\n</form>\r\n\r\n','Wordpress Plugin: J